dn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">z1b</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>President-elect Trump just won the election and it is causing a lot of volatility in the REIT market.</p> <p>Some of our positions are surging while others are taking a hit, resulting in opportunities to buy the dip. </p> <p>Here</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4744579-buy-the-dip-2-reits-getting-way-too-cheap", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 17:00:00"}, {"id": "4745331", "title": "Bank of England Stays On Hold, But A Dovish Front Is Building", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"The Bank of England in London\" data-id=\"173224046\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3744px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">kelvinjay</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/francesco-pesole/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Francesco Pesole</a></em></p> <p>The Bank of England kept the Bank Rate at 4.75% today, as widely expected. Forward guidance remained very cautious and data-dependent, and the Monetary Policy Committee is explicitly refusing to commit to the size and timing of rate cuts in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745331-bank-of-england-stays-hold-dovish-front-building", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 16:55:00"}]}